Charles Schwab Platform Shows ETFs’ Increasing Popularity Among Investors


July 24, 2017, 05:16:52 PM EDT
By editor@etftrends.com (ETF Trends), Tom Lydon









































Shutterstock photo


The exchange traded fund universe continues to expand as   Charles Schwab  data reveals increased demand for the cheap and efficient investment tool across all investor segments, along with rising appetite for low-cost Schwab products. According to a recent Charles Schwab research note of clients on the Charles Schwab platform, ETF assets at Schwab increased 29%… Click to read more at ETFtrends.com. 



